            <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\gpio\trident_gpio_overview.xml" xtrc="p:3;55:27">GPIO instances from <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\gpio\trident_gpio_overview.xml" xtrc="b:1;57:30">4 to 37 </b>and <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\gpio\trident_gpio_overview.xml" xtrc="b:2;59:30">49 to 109 </b>can only be used as on-chip GPIOs. GPIOs instances from <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\gpio\trident_gpio_overview.xml" xtrc="b:3;61:30">0 to 3 </b>and <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\gpio\trident_gpio_overview.xml" xtrc="b:4;63:30">38 to 48 </b>are reserved for TWI_0, SPI_Flash_0, and UART_0 Interfaces.</p>
